title: Imgur Not Loading on Mobile (Android) Private Tab
content: I have Firefox as my default browser and set it to open links in private tabs, but imgur will not load either the home page or a specific link in private. I have tried turning off enhanced tracking protection in private as well, but no luck (see attached image). The odd thing is imgur will load in the non-private tab, but not private. I run ublock origin in both private and non-private. I am using firefox for android version 117.0 on a Samsung Galaxy S23+.
creator: Nerlen_Poi
